    public class PanelViewParameterSet
extends Object
implements org.ascape.runtime.swing.navigator.PanelViewProvider, ActionListener
    Provides a PanelView based on a ParameterSet. The PanelView contains a table of the ParameterSet as well as update and reset/default buttons.
